stories.text: "CommerceCX’s Contract Pricing enables a single source of truth about product pricing. This module provides you with the best price for any product configuration customer-wise. Our Contract Pricing solution maintains pricing information at the regional and country levels. It applies pricing rules based on multiple variables, including tiers, units of measure, duration, one-time, and subscription to customer and contract-specific pricing"
